data.description: UPDATED 12/14/23 PROBATE SALE - COURT DATE IS SET FOR JANUARY 24TH 2024.  WILL BE ACCECPTING OFFERS STARTING MID JANUARY. Here is the deal with this Home.  Beautifully located in the Creekside neighborhood of Shadow Ridge, NO HOA or Mello-ROOS.  Home needs lots of TLC and new appliances, some windows, paint etc.  It is evident that CATS lived unsupervised in the house.  The house was professionally cleaned, but there is still cat odor in the air.  Good Neighborhood, Good Price, and with a little TLC could be a Great Family Home.Property being sold in current condition, SELLERS WILL NOT REPAIR, REPLACE OR CREDIT BUYER.
